<normalizedToken id="07EA26B7AD839289F373ECDD1AC2FB66" originalValue="Medellín">Medellin</normalizedToken>
, rd. to San Pedro, 13.ii.1983, O.S. Flint, Jr. (USNM 104529) (NMNH). Paratypes: Same data as holotype, 2 males, 1 female (NMNH); COLOMBIA: Antioquia: Quebrada Agua Mala, 34 km NW 
<normalizedToken id="ABDB04E2790C1153990DBDB79C08B495" originalValue="Medellín">Medellin</normalizedToken>
