<normalizedToken id="827E87F686B289DAAEBA604BAA03CE40" originalValue="Medellín">Medellin</normalizedToken>
, rd. to San Pedro, 20.ii.1984, C.M. and O.S. Flint, Jr., 1 male (NMNH); Quebrada La 
<normalizedToken id="6FFD7445E293E881C4A44E543EB9B7B7" originalValue="Ayurá">Ayura</normalizedToken>
above Envigado, 21.ii.1984, C.M. and O.S. Flint, Jr., 1 male (NMNH); Quebrada La 
<normalizedToken id="0184D72F99C77586736063DB44453E95" originalValue="Ayurá">Ayura</normalizedToken>
